low' style='-webkit-text-decoration:underline #2346ea;color:#2346ea;text-decoration:underline #2346ea;'>led to a surge</a></span><span style=''> in LINK's value, with a leap of over 20% following the announcement.</span></p></div><style>   p span[style*='font-size'] { line-height: 1.6; } </style><div style='padding-bottom:16px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:6px;'><p style='color:#222222;color:var(--wt-text-on-background-color) !important;font-family:'Helvetica',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:26px;text-align:left;'><span style=''><b>In other news, </b></span><span style=''>Uniswap also unveiled some updates themselves, but UNI didn’t budge a bit—probably because everything they offered were similarly available in other platforms like </span><span style=''><a class='link' href='https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovLzFpbmNoLmlvL2Z1c2lvbi8_.ukMsgk9JKcoMSKcoEwjjhocXnIB0h1U3MK8ECSrE2-k' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer nofollow' style='-webkit-text-decoration:underline #2346ea;color:#2346ea;text-decoration:underline #2346ea;'>1inch Fusion</a></span><span style=''>.</span></p></div></div>",
